metadata.name: ElonMusk & memes fans gNFT #1
metadata.description: This project is for those who are fans of Elon Musk and memes. There are also funny faces and moments in the collection. Some pieces will be very valuable given their rarity. Either way, it's pretty cool to own an NFT like this. Don't wait for the moment when Elon Musk posts about it. Because then it will be too late to buy. The roadmap also includes the fact that the associated website will be continuously developed. We aim to be one of the largest Elon Musk and meme fan groups. How fanatic are you?
